column5: Hi Guys,  Looking for 2 more guys Salmon/Trout Charter fishing with Fishhunter for Sunday, June 6.  PM me for details.
bump  you guys will have a great time

Nestor, if it wasn't for musky opener and wanting to get out in my own boat (only used it three times this year, so far)  I would have gladly joined you guys.  Maybe another time.  Good luck out there!!
Thanks Frankie! Hope we can hook up again soon. Good luck with musky opener. BTW I spoke to my neighbor, he said he saw our walleye pics. Such a small world.
Ok, 4 seats filled - daking_eh2007, dennis, jet and frozen-fire. See you guys at port hope on sunday, jun 6 at 5am.
